text: Indian rojak, not fresh, food has turned sour. Tofu is mushy even though it's fried before serving.

I am very surprised with tonight's experience. I had an craving for Naan and Garlic and we ordered 5 pieces with 2 recommended curry Butter Chicken and Kadai Chicken. And yes we finished everything. Savoury and hits the right spot! The Butter Chicken is so well cooked with vegetables and the Kadai Chicken is so flavourful! We ended up tabao our Tulang Merah home cos the Naan is so big! Yes the price is a bit steep but each curry serving is good for 2 too! Will definitely recommend all to try in this small Chai Chee town centre!

Rude staff. If don't prefer to run shop ,better close the shop.Make sarcastic joke on payment method eventhough have cashless transaction. Last visit for this shop and will share to other friends of mine to avoid this place at all cost.
Overcharged price for food compared to others in the Kembangan Chai Chee area. Staff was rude. Food takeaway we ordered was given wrong. Overall bad experience and horrendous service.
